You have to install libinput package then you can set it also in the menu 
Just look for libinput 

Then run:

libinput-gestures-setup status

to learn about the status

Then start the program 

libinput-gestures-setup start

and enable it as autostart 

libinput-gestures-setup autostart

done!

then you can edit your gestures with libinput in the menu bar 
